# value calculation

    it calculate for each value record. 
    one thumb up adding up one, one thumb down deleting one value.

    so there are data structure to log these value changes:
    
      value record : {
        value: {
          up: { 
            user name : { info },
            user name : { info }, ... 
          },

          down: { 
            user name : { info },
            user name : { info }, ... 
          },


        }
      }


    We need operations: 

    initialize value data structure for a record,
    thumb up/add one positive
    thumb down/add one negative

    count the result:
      positive number - negative number OR up - down



